      "rationale": "Independent analyst review conducted by second team member at each of the three institutions. Model setup checklists completed and archived. Boundary condition application and load application verified against ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry. No use errors identified. Cross-laboratory consistency of FEA setup confirmed through round-robin comparison."
