      "rationale": "Material properties (E, yield stress, UTS) sourced from ASTM F136 Ti-6Al-4V coupon testing (N=8 coupons). Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of actual screws (N=5). Input uncertainty distributions (normal for E, lognormal for yield stress) propagated via Monte Carlo (documented in hasUncertaintyQuantification links). Confidence in material inputs is explicitly rated low-to-moderate due to batch-to-batch variability; wide UQ bounds are the honest consequence and are fully documented. Gradation 2 met through probabilistic input characterization."
