      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 protocol followed at both laboratories. Load rate, fixture geometry, displacement measurement instrumentation, and environmental conditions (ambient temperature, humidity) documented per protocol. Single test condition (static compression-bending only) is a recognized scope limitation acknowledged in the COU description. However, the single condition is the COU-relevant condition; fatigue and torsion are outside scope of this COU. Within the defined COU, test conditions are fully characterized and replicated across laboratories, meeting Gradation 2."
