      "rationale": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions) mapped directly to measured experimental parameters. CMM-measured screw geometry used as FEA geometry inputs. Measured material coupon properties (same production lot) used as FEA material inputs. Fixture stiffness measured and incorporated as boundary condition. Equivalency mapping table documented and reviewed. No unmatched parameters identified. Gradation 2 achieved."
